        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pink Tax Repeal Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;This bill prohibits any person from selling (or offering to sell) substantially similar consumer products or services&amp;nbsp;at different prices based on the gender of the intended purchaser. If, for example, the only difference between two products is the color, they are substantially similar.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill provides authority for the Federal Trade Commission and state attorneys general to enforce these requirements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!--tinycomments|2.1|data:application/json;base64,--&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
